{"tid":1655611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［請推上熱門］正處於憤怒 仇恨 無助嘅巴打入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:09:26.000Z","uid":54640,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"358c9c96dde2259a9be140b9a310793856080355","tid":1655611,"uid":54640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"見到連登開始成為行動post集中地<br />\n越嚟越多人有唔同意見<br />\n亦都開始有分歧<br />\n有人努力包容唔同意見<br />\n有人惡言惡語<br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n請大家對自己手足互相尊重！！！<br />\n<br />\n各位手足都係由四個月前慢慢進化<br />\n每人有快有慢 有勇有智<br />\n大家都好叻 四個月前嘅大家都冇諗過今時今日可以走到呢個地步<br />\n但係最近見到越嚟越多互屌嘅post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足係你朋友嚟架！<br />\n請對每位手足互相尊重！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以家越嚟越多分化撚 五毛撚<br />\n佢哋最想睇到嘅就係你地內哄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你地嘈得越勁 越亂 佢地越開心</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以懇請大家善待自己手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1）大家想發表意見前 請諗一諗啲說話會唔會對手足做成言語傷害</strong></span><br />\n勸導時請注意語氣 請勿一嚟就問候人老母<br />\n點戇鳩都好 始終都係你手足<br />\n人地同你有意見分歧時 要保持冷靜應對<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>切忌係咪都一開口屌人老母<br />\n唔好以為係連登隱藏身份就為所欲為</strong></span><br />\n人地老母同你好熟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你對自己兄弟都唔會咁講啦<br />\n面對一開口就出言不遜嘅人 請一開始以禮相待<br />\n仲係咁口臭就唔駛覆佢 等佢自已單機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>2）請善用不推文回覆</strong></span><br />\n遇到膠post/意見唔啱嘅post 請勿一開始屌人老母先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以用不推文回覆嘗試同樓豬溝通<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同樓豬唔啱嘴形就block/無視佢 盡量減少衝突</strong></span><br />\n等其他有耐性嘅巴打再勸導佢 唔好正面衝突<br />\n成個連登都粗口橫飛郁啲就問候人 外人睇起嚟好鬼肉酸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>3）開post前前請三思</strong></span><br />\n如非必要 請唔好出post屌自己友<br />\n同1）一樣<br />\n但係開post者有更大責任諗清楚開post嘅目的係乜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>4）多讚美 多推行動post</strong></span><br />\n請大大力讚揚開行動post嘅手足 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">辛苦曬 多謝你 加油</span></strong> 呢啲說話一啲都唔難講出口<br />\n請保持正能量釋放 等手足更加有動力開post<br />\n其實大家都可以做到 簡單一句溫暖人心 比外人知道大家有教養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係個句 請大家保持批判思考<br />\n停一停 諗一諗<br />\n唔好比人咁易帶到風向<br />\n做個智勇雙全嘅巴打<br />\n囡囡見到都濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a5300e14e768e2cd0c908d517c5f37eed2ffb4d9","tid":1655611,"uid":54640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsVup1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsVup1z.jpg&h=976c1f42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFuOFzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFuOFzV.jpg&h=f3e4ee13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bc320760dc318f599824deeabd8ff8b500fcafb","tid":1655611,"uid":54640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30VkAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30VkAM.jpg&h=32585c4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3d550e2c1d82daac6242a69c3136ce573265247","tid":1655611,"uid":54640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpicnPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpicnPz.jpg&h=9cc98f94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DiUKYnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDiUKYnV.jpg&h=9795a2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D44OFBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD44OFBg.jpg&h=211a